high_descs: Turn left and go to the microwave on the counter on the right.
Pick up the gray knife on the counter behind the brown bowl.
Turn around and go towards the end of the wooden table on the right.
Slice the bread on the left near the edge on the table.
Place the knife on the table behind the sliced bread.
Take the end slice of the bread from the table.
Turn right and go to the sink and turn left.
Remove the bread after heating it in the microwave.
Move forward and turn right towards the counter on the right of the microwave
Place the bread on the counter behind the brown bowl on the right of the microwave.

Place the slice of bread on top of the counter.
